{"tid":531061,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傑斯畀老竇鬧爆！唔配執教威爾斯 E-mail 此主題給朋友","createTime":"2018-01-16T11:51:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T09:08:54.000Z","uid":30788,"like":64,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"efd8d5a6cab3d297f07585ee67101881f9f151c7","tid":531061,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T11:51:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/attachments/day_180116/20180116_237a56c6fabef926b228Bn9f73IMHqI5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_180116%2F20180116_237a56c6fabef926b228Bn9f73IMHqI5.jpg&h=c0d0050f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n傑斯終於再就業成為威爾斯國家隊領隊，不過大家應該記得，佢曾經被揭發偷嗒細佬老婆，即使佢球員時代喺曼聯有幾好波，倫理道德上都係賤男1個，就連佢老竇丹尼威爾遜都話：「我甚至唔想提起佢個名，只係想用嗰個前球員稱呼佢。作為長子，佢本應照顧細佬，而唔係背後插刀，佢用最差嘅方式欺騙家人，又唔能夠似番個男人咁去道歉，我真係想去記者會同佢對質，因為佢配唔上呢份工作，威爾斯領隊應該由受尊敬嘅人去擔任。」至於傑斯姑媽，就講得更入肉：「威爾斯球員要將老婆鎖晒入屋，傑斯喺卡迪夫有幾百個親人，但冇人想佢返嚟，佢真係令人好扯火。」 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180116/bkn-20180116165822982-0116_00882_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180116%2Fbkn-20180116165822982-0116_00882_001.html&d=1XqBj0AsuG9BAg1bToNApb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=3d3990cb\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180116/bkn-20180116165822982-0116_00882_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"32866898ac9f75930b7d95ec8c967e47933614dd","tid":531061,"uid":4586,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T11:53:00.000Z","msg":"記仇架<br />\n最聯做野都指指點點"},{"pid":"ffcc2bad927de3b8e38719748793f59e6245c63d","tid":531061,"uid":34457,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"32866898ac9f75930b7d95ec8c967e47933614dd","tid":531061,"uid":4586,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T11:53:00.000Z","msg":"記仇架<br />\n最聯做野都指指點點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T11:54:42.000Z","msg":"皇者做野唔使你班仆街冚家鏟教！"},{"pid":"28fcad7deb2b8ae7fe28a760b7787d85394f4235","tid":531061,"uid":9120,"like":4,"dislike":1,